PANAMA; AMERICANS -- PANAMA; UNITED STATES -- ARMED FORCES -- PANAMA; UNITED 
STATES -- FOREIGN INVESTMENTS -- PANAMA; NORIEGA, MANUEL A 
</P>
</SUBJECT>
