<SUBJECT>
<P>
CONSTITUTIONAL AMENDMENTS; FLAGS; DESECRATION; LEGISLATION -- UNITED STATES; 
FREEDOM OF SPEECH; TEXAS -- LAWS; CRANSTON, ALAN 
</P>
