Tuesday's devastating quake, struggled toward normalcy. But some, like JoAnn 
Lopez, above, endured a painful wait as rescuers sifted through the rubble of a 
missing friend's San Francisco apartment. Sacramento Bee; Drawing, REPAIRING 
THE BAY BRIDGE, PAUL GONZALES / Los Angeles Times 
</P>
</GRAPHIC>
